COPYRIGHT 2004 BLUE CROSS/BLUE SHIELD OF KANSAS CITY 
COPYRIGHT 2005 BLUE CROSS/BLUE SHIELD OF KANSAS CITY 


JOB NAME:     IdsNdcFkey

DESCRIPTION:     Takes the sorted file and applies the Foreign key.  
      

INPUTS:  File from IdsNdcPkey
	
  
HASH FILES:     hf_recycle - contains records that had errors on them for recycle.  Recycle is not used in this program - file is completely updated from Facets each time.


TRANSFORMS:  GetFkeyCodes for diagnosis category code
                                 
                           Unknown and Not Applicable rows are created - all rows are sent through collector to combine into output file
                           

PROCESSING:  This job would be run whenever there is an update to the NDC table/file.  

OUTPUTS:  NDC.#Source#.dat

MODIFICATIONS:
            Steph Goddard  08/2004  -   Originally Programmed
            BJ Luce             06/15/2005 - changed for rx deductibles 
            BJ Luce             10/31/2005 - add new fields
                                                            use FDB for source system for code mapping lookups
                                                            use UWS for source system for code mapping lookup for DSM drug type code
           BJ Luce             04/2006         use environment variables, use Source in output
           Bhoomi              03/29/2007    Added new field to the table called NDC_RTE_TYP_CD_SK by directly mapping to GCRT2, which is brought from RROUTED3_ROUTE_DESC and looking up at NDC ROUTE TYPE domain                                                             from code mapping table in foreign key process.























































